org.apache.calcite.rel.hint

类 HintStrategyTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.calcite.rel.hint.HintStrategyTable

  • public class HintStrategyTable
extends Object
    A collections of HintStrategys.

    Every supported hint should register a HintPredicate into this collection. For example, HintPredicates.JOIN implies that this hint would be propagated and attached to the Join relational expressions.

    Match of hint name is case in-sensitive.

    另请参阅:
    HintPredicate
